data.body:
When trying to comment out a line using command-/, Atom throws an exception.

I was inside this .scss file.

``` scss
@import "../globals";

/* TOKEN */

#token{
  max-width: 600px;
  padding: 10px 40px 40px 40px;
  margin: 0 auto;

  h2{
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
  }

  h2 img{
    margin-right: 15px;
    width: 48px;
    border: #d1d1d1 3px solid;
  }

  .user-token{
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: $linkColor;
    background-color: #e7e7e7;
    border: #d4d4d4 2px solid;

    padding: 10px
  }

}
```
